{"word":"ἀποτολμάω","slug":"ἀποτολμάω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<p ><strong><elT>ἀποτολμάω</elT></strong> (s. <elT><a class='T' href='S:τολμάω'>τολμάω</a></elT>; <a href=\"#_ftn1\" name=\"_ftnref1\">Thu</a>. <a href=\"#_ftn2\" name=\"_ftnref2\">et al.</a>; <a href=\"#_ftn3\" name=\"_ftnref3\">Polyb</a>.; <a href=\"#_ftn4\" name=\"_ftnref4\">Diod S</a>; <a href=\"#_ftn5\" name=\"_ftnref5\">Plut</a>.; <a href=\"#_ftn6\" name=\"_ftnref6\">SIG</a> 1169, 94; <a href=\"#_ftn7\" name=\"_ftnref7\">BGU</a> 1574, 22; <a href=\"#_ftn8\" name=\"_ftnref8\">PLond</a> IV, 1343, 42; <a href=\"#_ftn9\" name=\"_ftnref9\">Philo</a>, Post. Cai. 42; <a href=\"#_ftn10\" name=\"_ftnref10\">Jos.</a>, C. Ap. 2, 180) <strong><em>be bold</em></strong> <a href=\"#_ftn11\" name=\"_ftnref11\">abs.</a> <el>Ἠσαΐας ἀποτολμᾷ καὶ λέγει</el> <em>Isaiah is so bold as to say</em> <strong><a class='B' href='B:520 10:20'>Ro 10:20</a></strong> (<a href=\"#_ftn12\" name=\"_ftnref12\">cp.</a> <a href=\"#_ftn13\" name=\"_ftnref13\">Demosth</a>. 19, 199 <el>τολμήσει … καὶ ἐρεῖ</el>).—<a href=\"#_ftn14\" name=\"_ftnref14\">DELG</a> <a href=\"#_ftn15\" name=\"_ftnref15\">s.v.</a> <el>τόλμη</el>. <a href=\"#_ftn16\" name=\"_ftnref16\">TW</a>.</p>"}]}